OL,3,CHospital 'putting patients at risk'
OL,4,Ctold to improve by inspectors
OL,6,FPatients are at "risk of unsafe
OL,7,Ftreatment" at the Royal Cornwall
OL,8,FHospital, according to health
OL,9,Finspectors.
OL,11,FInspectors from the Care Quality
OL,12,FCommission (CQC) visited the hospital
OL,13,Fand found "ongoing challenges" were
OL,14,Faffecting people's care.
OL,16,FAn inspection of urgent and emergency
OL,17,Fservices and medical care at the
OL,18,Fhospital found breaches in regulations
OL,19,Frelating to dignity and respect, safe
OL,20,Fcare and treatment, safe premises,
OL,21,Fstaffing and management processes.
