OL,3,CHospital 'putting patients at risk'
OL,4,Ctold to improve by inspectors
OL,6,FThe CQC has again rated Royal Cornwall
OL,7,FHospitals NHS Trust as requires
OL,8,Fimprovement.
OL,10,FThis comes after inspections carried
OL,11,Fout in April, which revealed that
OL,12,Fwards lacked appropriate safety
OL,13,Fequipment and staff did not
OL,14,Fconsistently store or manage medicines
OL,15,Fsafely.
OL,17,FThe CQC found "ongoing challenges that
OL,18,Faffected people's care", such as "poor
OL,19,Fenvironmental design and clutter" and
OL,20,Fbeds placed without call bells.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
