OL,6,FIn urgent and emergency care,
OL,7,Finspectors also found that staff often
OL,8,Fleft opened medicines without revised
OL,9,Fexpiry dates, with the preparation
OL,10,Farea unsecured and at child height.
OL,12,FCatherine Campbell, CQC's deputy
OL,13,Fdirector of operations in Cornwall,
OL,14,Fexplained: "In both medical and
OL,15,Femergency services, staffing shortages
OL,16,Fand reliance on temporary staff
OL,17,Fdisrupted continuity of care.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
