OL,3,CHospital 'putting patients at risk'
OL,4,Ctold to improve by inspectors
OL,6,F"Flow and capacity pressures also had
OL,7,Fa direct impact: transfers to
OL,8,Fescalation areas, long waits for ward
OL,9,Fbeds, and crowding in emergency
OL,10,Fdepartments meant people waited longer
OL,11,Fthan necessary, sometimes in
OL,12,Fenvironments that didn't meet their
OL,13,Fneeds or support their privacy and
OL,14,Fdignity.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
