OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F431A1756469145
OL,3,CHospital 'putting patients at risk'
OL,4,Ctold to improve by inspectors
OL,6,F"We also found risks in how staff
OL,7,Fmanaged medicines, including expired
OL,8,Fstock, poor labelling, and incomplete
OL,9,Fmedicine records which created the
OL,10,Fpotential for errors, putting people
OL,11,Fat risk of unsafe treatment. Leaders'
OL,12,Foversight and risk management
OL,13,Fprocesses didn't always work well,
OL,14,Fwith delays in investigations and
OL,15,Fincomplete reviews."
OL,17,FHowever, the CQC also found "some
OL,18,Fpositive practise".
