OL,3,CHospital 'putting patients at risk'
OL,4,Ctold to improve by inspectors
OL,6,FMs Campbell added: "Staff worked in
OL,7,Fstrong partnership with others. In
OL,8,Fmedical care, their links with
OL,9,Fcommunity teams, discharge
OL,10,Fcoordinators, and the integrated care
OL,11,Fsystem supported people to leave
OL,12,Fhospital more safely and without
OL,13,Funnecessary delay.
OL,15,F"In emergency care, specialist teams
OL,16,Fsuch as learning disability services,
OL,17,Fhomeless advisors, and mental health
OL,18,Fliaison were well integrated, helping
OL,19,Fpeople receive joined-up care that met
OL,20,Ftheir wider needs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
