OL,3,CHospital 'putting patients at risk'
OL,4,Ctold to improve by inspectors
OL,6,F"We also saw a culture of learning and
OL,7,Fsafety. Staff in medical care shared
OL,8,Flearning at safety briefings and team
OL,9,Fevents, while in emergency care,
OL,10,Fproactive reporting of incidents and
OL,11,Fcomplaints led to improvements. This
OL,12,Fmeant people benefited from staff who
OL,13,Fwere constantly adapting and learning
OL,14,Ffrom past events to improve care.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
