OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F431A1756469145
OL,3,CHospital 'putting patients at risk'
OL,4,Ctold to improve by inspectors
OL,6,F"Despite pressures, staff remained
OL,7,Fcommitted to treating people with
OL,8,Fcompassion, dignity, and respect. They
OL,9,Fcommunicated clearly with people and
OL,10,Ftheir carers, involving them in
OL,11,Fdecisions even in busy and challenging
OL,12,Fenvironments.
OL,14,F"Senior leaders were aware of the
OL,15,Fissues and supported their teams to
OL,16,Fprioritise safety. The trust
OL,17,Frecognises where it must improve, and
OL,18,Fwe will continue to work with them and
OL,19,Freturn to check progress."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
